(26, 1, '2026-07-07 03:43:50', '2026-07-07 03:43:50', 'The Logitech Mechanical Gaming Keyboard is designed for gamers, professionals, and everyday users who demand reliable performance from their keyboards. Featuring USB / Wireless 2.4GHz, this product delivers consistent quality backed by Logitech\'s reputation for durable, well-engineered computer accessories. Specifications: Connectivity: USB / Wireless 2.4GHz; Switch Type: Mechanical Blue/Red; Backlight: RGB 16.8M colors; Layout: Full-size / TKL / 60%; Anti-Ghosting: Yes. Comes with manufacturer warranty and TechHub\'s 7-day replacement guarantee.', 'Logitech Mechanical Gaming Keyboard', 'Logitech Mechanical Gaming Keyboard - premium keyboard built for performance and reliability. Backed by Logitech\'s quality standards.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'logitech-mechanical-gaming-keyboard', '', '', '2026-07-07 03:48:38', '2026-07-07 03:48:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/techhub/?post_type=product&#038;p=26', 0, 'product', '', 0),
